comments: Great song!

Black Math has such good memories for me. Buying Elephant way back in '03 (10 years ago, wow!), learning the whole record when I was still learning guitar, then and a few years later jamming this song with one of my best friends on guitar having just met him. And it's just a raw and perfect track!
